local red = 0 local green = 0
function onReceiveOSC(msg) local name = msg[1] local val = tonumber(msg[2][1].value)
if (string.sub(name, -1) == "1") then red = val elseif (string.sub(name, -1) == "2") then green = val end
local color = Color(1)
if (green > 0) then color = Color(0, 1, 0) elseif (red > 0) then color = Color(1, 0, 0) end
for i=1,3 do local label = self.parent:findByName(tostring(i), false) if (label) then label.properties.textColor = color end end end
